The '''1994 Qatar Open''', known as the '''1994 Qatar [[Mobil]] Open''' for sponsorship reasons, was an ATP tournament held in [[Doha]], [[Qatar]]. The tournament was held from January 3 to January 10.

[[Stefan Edberg]] won his first title of the year and the 39th of his career.

