The '''2019 [[East Asian Youth Games]]''' will be an [[international]] [[multi-sport event]] for countries in [[East Asia]] .

== Participating nations ==
All eight countries whose [[National Olympic Committee]] is recognized by the [[East Asian Games Association]] and one country whose National Olympic Committee is recognized by the Oceania National Olympic Committees, would have participated had the games not been cancelled.<ref name="host" />
